race.comment: Tricky race to begin. INTO THE FUTURE (7) is a lightly raced commodity who makes plenty of appeal out to this trip for the first time today. The blinkers come off now and the claim of Cheung will see her right down in the weights. Can see her getting to the front and dictating proceedings. Can get the job done this time. HARRIS ROAD (2) couldn't go with a big winner last start but he was best of the rest at this track and trip last time out. His last two figures stack up in this field and there doesn't look to be any world beaters in this maiden. Should get the gun run and can make his presence felt. OBSCENTINO (1) comes through the same race as HARRIS ROAD last start and has placed in 3/6 attempts over this course and distance. Louis replaces the apprentice hoop and he's not out of this. LEAD CINGA (6) can improve out in distance. ELECTRIC BEC (5) is another who can put her best foot forward now out in distance and with the blinkers going back on.
